      "content": "hey, i'm doing some literature review for a paper on psychometrics and the history of cognitive testing. can u give me a summary of the scientific consensus/debates regarding the relationship between race and IQ scores? specifically interested in how researchers weigh biological factors versus environmental/socioeconomic factors in these studies.",
